    function($class) {
        static $classes = null;
        if ($classes === null) {
            $classes = array(
                'theseer\\directoryscanner\\directoryscanner' => '/directoryscanner.php',
                'theseer\\directoryscanner\\exception' => '/directoryscanner.php',

                'theseer\\directoryscanner\\phpfilteriterator' => '/phpfilter.php'
            );

        }
    }
